name: complex_if_mul_common_right_factor
section: control-if-arithmetic
args: cond:Bool common:Int a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Multiplying a common right operand across an if expression must choose branchwise products.
law: (= (fuzz-mul (if {cond} {a} {b}) {common}) (if {cond} (fuzz-mul {a} {common}) (fuzz-mul {b} {common})))
